{"tid":1575422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「出殯大遊行」十月一日有共識未？","createTime":"2019-09-17T00:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T18:41:49.000Z","uid":152455,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8a6bfe82344903b93d092df6856b66ce8d60bcdb","tid":1575422,"uid":152455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T00:56:21.000Z","msg":"距離國慶得返<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兩個禮拜</span></span>，點解仲未有當日活動文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />929全球反納粹遊行又係咪堅？有冇海外巴絲搞緊？ 全部野都好似未有共識咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只係知G20 登報搞得成，其他賀壽活動咩都未firm,不如盡快共識個日要做咩野啦，文宣都要時間架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我提議先： <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">英美旗海大遊行+黑白五星旗出殯大遊行、全民白衫素服、全民燒街衣、擺車頭相大慢駛</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166101210d3dfe3261aa8fe3c8c25338130bd2a2","tid":1575422,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T00:57:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全民徐步高民主look</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">200萬人送中國殯</span></span>"},{"pid":"007651e67eee35a61451dd2d7cf749d2ac0a3d20","tid":1575422,"uid":152455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"166101210d3dfe3261aa8fe3c8c25338130bd2a2","tid":1575422,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T00:57:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全民徐步高民主look</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">200萬人送中國殯</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:00:46.000Z","msg":"咁又唔好，咪等如咒自己老豆老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />白衫拎大頭相（習種？）算啦"},{"pid":"45ee475b62f28a4db99bfc47f214efda98d687fd","tid":1575422,"uid":152455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:16:15.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"fefa140e3c4459782b76690fb1d92d4ffe830ccc","tid":1575422,"uid":284264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:22:21.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n正呀"},{"pid":"9937af7bc7635d442af7edac6bb5d968c47bd8ae","tid":1575422,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:25:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4527d305e6d6e0e877e38f1257d05d88af399582","tid":1575422,"uid":278786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T18:41:49.000Z","msg":"如何做到有一百萬人以上，對和理非而言，最重要是諗到不用申請不反對通知書而且有合法途徑。否則乜文宣都無用。<br />\n<br />\n有條橋，就是抄何妖，佢話921清潔香港不用申請不反對通知書，仲串到撤銷遊行申請。<br />\n咁佢無被人拉無人告，心理上就可以宣傳：我地9.29/10.1搞的都是清潔香港行動，沿港島電車路線，人人執拉圾。<br />\n<br />\n人流控制方面：<br />\n可以呼籲港島人在自己區清潔；<br />\n九龍東人在鰂魚涌的香港殯儀館（象徵送中）以東，新界東人在鰂魚涌以西;<br />\n九龍西人在中環遮打花園以西，新界西人在中環以東。<br />\n<br />\n另一個重點，係需要有號召力的人或機構呼籲，大肆宣傳，俾和理非感覺既合法又多人陪，咁就安心參加。<br />\n<br />\n利申：和理非"}]}